reviews.text: Food is absolutely incredible in a warm and very local atmosphere. I would recommend to go with a chinese speaker though, to get the most out of this delicate place.

This place isn't cheap.  It has a Michelin star.  The food are good as expected.  It has both traditional Cantonese and Shanghaiese Dim Sum, which isn't common in Hong Kong.  The environment is very nice.  Staffs are friendly.  It is just a little bit hard to find if you have never been to this place.  It isn't typical for me to get lost, but I almost did looking for this place

reviews.text: 主廚卓越的廚藝在菜品上可見，烤鴨香脆可口，搭配其醬料可說是絕配，值得專程前往享用，總體來說極為推薦。
Food is absolutely incredible in a warm and very local atmosphere. I would recommend to go with a chinese speaker though, to get the most out of this delicate place.
這裡的食物質素十分好，而價格可能還比連鎖的蘇杭，上海菜館還要平，但茶錢略為高一點，一個聲稱是陳年普洱的薟茶要五十元一位， 但茶的質素 只是平平。

This place isn't cheap.  It has a Michelin star.  The food are good as expected.  It has both traditional Cantonese and Shanghaiese Dim Sum, which isn't common in Hong Kong.  The environment is very nice.  Staffs are friendly.  It is just a little bit hard to find if you have never been to this place.  It isn't typical for me to get lost, but I almost did looking for this place
裝修環境非常舒服是主菜，食品ok la. 一般般的上海餐！價錢就比較貴！

result.name: Marco Polo Hongkong Hotel

reviews.text: Good location which close to the shopping mall and harbour front. Nice view in room and worth to pay little more for upgrade to continental club. The food during cocktail is yummy. You can't eat those in other hotel club, such us pasta, noodle, peking duck. This is not my first time stay in club room, the staff always friendly and professional.  They remember me which make me feel like home. Compare other 5 stars hotel, I like to stay in Continental club because of the warm service.

Good location which closed to star ferry and shopping mall. Easy access to everywhere. Room is big compare with other hotels in HK. Club staffs are nice and friendly. They helped to book the table and give a good idea of local restaurants. The food in club lounge is yummy and nice.
The hotel was a Classic five stars hotel with decent hotel service. I love the service in the front.that was so energetic. Room was big compared to other hotels.in Hong Kong

Good accessibility, ferry and bus stop closed to hotel, Biggest shopping mall under hotel, if look for designer brands there you are.  Always long queue at lobby. Luck I booked the room at Continental club floor, personal check-in & out, private lounge and staff are friendly there.    Feel warm as home, compare the five star hotel with stylish cool service, I recommend the warm service in club.  Staff treat   me as family and friends. First choice for me in Hong Kong,
Fantastic staying experience that I am celebrating my girlfriend  birthday in the hotel. They arranged us a birthday cake and sing a birthday song for my girlfriend. Unbelievable hood!

result.name: 馬哥孛羅香港酒店

reviews.text:
立地がよく、館内もトイレも部屋もどこも清潔でした。
徒歩で行けるとこになんでも揃っていてこまりません。駅も路線選べるし、スターフェリーにもすぐなのでどこに行くにもべんりでした。
接客も笑顔でスピーディーに素敵な接客でした。声かけもよくしてくださって見てくださってて安心感がありました。
いいホテルでした。

朋友帮忙预定行政楼层房间，真的物超所值。食品种类多，连北京烤鸭也有，不单服务生有效率，17楼女经理帮忙订餐安排行程，退房快捷，服务一流. 下次来香港还要住这里
酒店地段很好，楼下就是海港城，环境不错，很方便，但眼见大堂排了长龙办理入住和退房, 
有预算值得推荐行政楼层
観光目的でしたので立地で選んだのですが正解でした。ショッピング、食事等とても便利な場所でした。ホテルの部屋は少し古いですが広めでした。初めて香港に行く方にはお勧めです。あと気にしない人は良いのですが部屋のビューは予約の際確認しておきましょう！

Good location which close to the shopping mall and harbour front. Nice view in room and worth to pay little more for upgrade to continental club. The food during cocktail is yummy. You can't eat those in other hotel club, such us pasta, noodle, peking duck. This is not my first time stay in club room, the staff always friendly and professional.  They remember me which make me feel like home. Compare other 5 stars hotel, I like to stay in Continental club because of the warm service.
